    "name": "The Funnel",
    "steam_appid": 3164380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Funnel is a short and replayable underground narrative game, mixing branching dialogue and puzzle minigames. What is the purpose of the factories? Why is the Funnel in your dreams? Why are the rules of this world falling apart? It's up to you to find out.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 3-5 hour story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 puzzle minigames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60k+ words of dialogue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ ways to reach the end</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/6e330afbe0a87fa895051a4df2f3b126.avif?t=1770153104\" width=1560 height=324 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Who do you trust</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose who to work with or who to betray. Every crew mate you meet has their own plan for the future of the factory, leading to different endings with entirely different minigames.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/f944c38fa6686a0256fe3c86ed7c74fa.poster.avif?t=1770153104\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/f944c38fa6686a0256fe3c86ed7c74fa.webm?t=1770153104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/f944c38fa6686a0256fe3c86ed7c74fa.mp4?t=1770153104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Minigames are choices</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just like your dialogue choices, succeeding or failing in a minigame will change the outcome of your story. If someone asks you to attach a timer to a bomb and you fail, that character might sacrifice themselves since the bomb no longer has a delay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/53b424bcc5638d8d894213a3cdc15bc7.poster.avif?t=1770153104\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/53b424bcc5638d8d894213a3cdc15bc7.webm?t=1770153104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/53b424bcc5638d8d894213a3cdc15bc7.mp4?t=1770153104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the mysteries that underpin this strange world</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience The Funnel’s unique world, diverging from our own timeline in the 1900s when a group of scientists in Old Philadelphia created the Funnel, a giant robotic structure that supposedly can average out the collective will of humanity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/5d0c9d14f1458f4f802dcb6b9579ed26.poster.avif?t=1770153104\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/5d0c9d14f1458f4f802dcb6b9579ed26.webm?t=1770153104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164380/extras/5d0c9d14f1458f4f802dcb6b9579ed26.mp4?t=1770153104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
